[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0776","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0776.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0520","title":"系统关键 NetBIOS/SMB 共享访问控制不当漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于系统关键的 NetBIOS/SMB 共享资源配置了不当的访问控制权限。攻击者可在无需身份认证的情况下，通过网络访问暴露的 SMB/NetBIOS 共享，读取或修改其中的敏感数据与系统资源。攻击条件为远程可达且共享权限过于宽松（如允许匿名或 Everyone 完全控制）。成功利用可导致敏感信息泄露与数据被篡改，影响系统机密性与完整性，CVSS v2 评分为 6.4（中危）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0520"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"检查并收紧所有系统关键 NetBIOS/SMB 共享的访问控制列表，禁止匿名与 Everyone 的写或完全控制权限，仅授予必要用户最小权限；关闭不需要的共享与 guest 账户，限制或禁用不必要的 SMB 服务与 139/445 端口对外开放，并按组织策略定期审计共享权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0520","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0520.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0776.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0766","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0766.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0512","title":"邮件服务器 SMTP 开放中继漏洞","description":"邮件服务器被显式配置为允许 SMTP 邮件中继（Open Relay），导致未经身份验证的第三方可通过该服务器转发垃圾邮件。攻击者利用此配置缺陷可大量发送垃圾邮件，消耗服务器资源并导致 IP 被列入黑名单，影响邮件服务的正常投递。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0512"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"关闭 SMTP 开放中继功能，配置邮件服务器仅允许经过身份验证的用户进行邮件中继，或限制中继仅针对受信任的域名和 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T20:32:30.154368254+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0512"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0766.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0641","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0641.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0401","title":"Linux Linux 内核 /proc 任意内存读取竞争条件漏洞","description":"Linux 2.2.1 内核的 /proc 文件系统中存在竞争条件漏洞。由于 /proc 文件系统在处理文件并发访问时未正确同步，本地攻击者可通过竞态条件读取内核任意内存数据，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Linux 2.2.1 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统账号权限方可触发，CVSS v2 评分为 3.7，危害等级低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0401"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"1999-01-01","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.2 或更高版本以消除 /proc 文件系统中的条件竞争漏洞。如无法升级内核，可限制不可信本地用户的登录权限并禁用无需使用的 /proc 文件系统挂载点。建议迁移至仍在维护的长期支持内核版本（如 4.x、5.x 或 6.x 系列），这些版本已彻底修复此类问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0641.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0639","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0639.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0399","title":"mIRC 5.5 DCC 服务器命令文件名过滤漏洞","description":"mIRC 5.5 客户端的 DCC 服务器命令在处理文件名时未正确过滤特殊字符（如路径遍历字符），远程攻击者可通过发送特制的 DCC 文件传输请求，将恶意文件写入目标系统的任意路径，进而可能实现任意命令执行。攻击者只需诱使目标用户接受恶意的 DCC 文件传输即可触发，无需认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0399"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 mIRC 至 5.5 以上版本。该漏洞已在后续版本中修复，建议用户升级到最新版本（当前为 7.84）以获取完整的安全修复和功能更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0399"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0639.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0634","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0634.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0395","title":"BackWeb Polite Agent Protocol 竞争条件漏洞","description":"BackWeb Polite Agent Protocol 中存在竞争条件漏洞。BackWeb 是一款用于向客户端推送软件更新的通信协议，其 Polite Agent 组件在处理服务器响应时存在时间窗口竞争问题。远程攻击者可通过网络向目标发送特制请求，在合法服务器响应到达前抢先注入伪造数据包，从而成功伪造 BackWeb 服务器身份。成功利用此漏洞可导致中间人攻击，攻击者能够向客户端推送恶意更新或窃取敏感信息。该漏洞利用复杂度较高，需要精确的时间控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0395"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"联系 BackWeb 厂商获取针对 Polite Agent Protocol 的安全补丁。由于该协议设计缺陷涉及竞争条件，建议在网络边界部署入侵检测系统，对 BackWeb 通信流量进行深度包检测。同时限制 BackWeb 客户端仅与可信服务器通信，并使用加密通道验证服务器身份。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:55:30.134314490+00:00","references":["http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise17.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0634.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0620","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0620.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0384","title":"Microsoft Visual Basic for Applications Forms 2.0 ActiveX 剪贴板信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Visual Basic for Applications 5.0 中捆绑的 Forms 2.0 ActiveX 控件存在安全漏洞，当用户访问包含 ActiveX 内容的文档时，该控件可被利用读取用户剪贴板中的文本数据，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者可通过构造恶意文档诱导用户打开，从而窃取剪贴板中可能包含的密码、信用卡号等敏感信息。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0384"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-001 提供的更新补丁，禁用不必要的 ActiveX 控件执行权限，在 Internet Explorer 中提高安全区域设置以限制 ActiveX 控件的自动运行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:08:18.779371312+00:00","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-001"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0620.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0488","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0294","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 WINS SNMP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 数据库通过 SNMP 协议可被远程攻击者删除所有记录，导致拒绝服务。攻击者无需认证即可通过 SNMP 发送恶意请求，删除 WINS 服务中的所有 NetBIOS 名称记录，造成网络名称解析服务瘫痪。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0294"],"sources":["cve","avd","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"1999-01-01","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全更新或禁用不必要的 SNMP 服务，限制 SNMP 访问权限，配置 SNMP 社区字符串为强密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0294","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0294","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0294"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0472","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0472.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0283","title":"Sun Java Web Server 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Sun Java Web Server 1.1 Beta 存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接请求 .jhtml 文件获取其原始源代码。该漏洞源于服务器对 .jhtml 文件的处理逻辑缺陷，未能正确解析执行而直接返回文件内容，导致 CGI 程序的源代码、数据库连接信息及业务逻辑等敏感数据暴露。攻击者只需发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0283"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Sun Java Web Server 1.1 正式版或更高版本（如 2.0），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在服务器配置中将 .jhtml 文件映射至 Java Servlet 处理器而非静态文件处理器，并禁止目录遍历。鉴于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 或 Apache Tomcat 等现代替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88256790401004&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20375","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0283","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0283.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8q69-243x-44f9/GHSA-8q69-243x-44f9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9ebd3145-ae01-469d-9fe2-ea9bfed3c14f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0472.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0472.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0472.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0412","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0412.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0226","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IP 分片拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统的 TCP/IP 协议栈在实现 IP 分片重组逻辑时存在缺陷，未能正确处理经过分片（fragmentation）的 IP 数据包，导致内核在处理畸形分片时出现资源耗尽或崩溃。攻击者可构造并发送特制的 IP 分片包序列，在无需身份认证的情况下远程触发目标系统的拒绝服务（DoS）状态，使受影响的 Windows NT 主机蓝屏重启或停止响应网络请求。该漏洞影响运行 TCP/IP 服务的 Windows NT 系列系统，远程可达即可利用，可导致关键服务长时间不可用。微软后续通过安全补丁修复了分片重组处理逻辑。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0226"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4（SP4）或更高版本，该补丁已修复 TCP/IP 协议栈对分片 IP 数据包处理不当的问题。若无法立即安装补丁，应在边界防火墙或路由器上过滤并丢弃入站的分片 IP 数据包（Fragment Offset 大于 0 的报文），禁止将此类碎片转发至内网主机；如该主机不作路由器使用，可关闭注册表 EnableRouting/EnableProxy 以禁用 IP 转发；同时部署入侵检测规则拦截 Teardrop 类畸形分片攻击，并仅开放必要的网络端口以缩小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0226"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0412.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0395","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0395.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0209","title":"SunOS 4.1.x SunView selection_svc 远程文件读取漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.x 系统自带的 SunView 图形环境提供的 selection_svc 服务存在未授权访问缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可连接该服务并读取目标主机上的任意文件内容。攻击条件为：目标主机运行 SunView 且开放 selection_svc 服务端口，攻击者处于可与其网络连通的位置。该漏洞可导致系统敏感信息（如口令文件、配置文件等）泄露，危害系统安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0209"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 SunOS 补丁版本，或禁用 SunView 的 selection_svc 服务并限制相关端口的网络访问，仅在受信任的内部网络中开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T08:26:46.410016186+00:00","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0209"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0395.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0172","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0585","title":"Windows NT/2000 默认管理员账户名配置缺陷漏洞","description":"Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统默认管理员账户名为「Administrator」，该已知账户名降低了暴力破解与字典攻击的难度。攻击者可利用该默认账户名对管理员账户实施密码爆破，进而尝试获取系统最高权限。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，影响所有采用默认安装配置的 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害较低但会削弱系统整体安全性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0585"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"建议立即将 Windows NT/2000 的默认管理员账户「Administrator」重命名为自定义名称，禁用该账户的远程交互式登录权限，并启用账户锁定策略与强密码复杂度要求，限制管理员组的网络访问范围，必要时应迁移至仍受安全支持的现代 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0585","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0585","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0585.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-01080","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-01080.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1080","title":"SunOS Solaris rmmount 特权提升漏洞","description":"SunOS 5.7 中的 rmmount 工具在挂载文件系统时未正确设置 nosuid 标志，与文档说明及先前版本行为不符。本地攻击者可通过物理访问插入包含 setuid 程序的软盘或 CD-ROM，运行 volcheck 触发自动挂载，从而获得 root 权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1080"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2024-06-01","remediation":"升级到 SunOS 5.7 的补丁版本，或在 rmmount.conf 中为所有可移动介质指定 nosuid 选项，防止 setuid 程序从外部介质执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-01T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1080"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-01080.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1369","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1369.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1159","title":"SSH 特权端口远程转发权限绕过漏洞","description":"SSH 2.0.11及更早版本存在权限验证缺失漏洞，本地用户无需root权限即可请求从特权端口（端口号小于1024）进行远程转发。该漏洞源于SSH服务未对端口转发请求进行充分的权限检查，允许低权限用户利用SSH的远程转发功能绑定到系统特权端口，从而可能绕过安全策略或提升本地权限。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用条件相对有限，但成功利用后可造成权限提升或网络访问控制绕过。该漏洞影响SSH 2.0.11及之前版本，CVSS评分4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1159"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.780","remediation":"升级到 SSH 2.0.12 或更高版本，该版本要求远程转发特权端口必须具有 root 权限。如无法升级，可在 sshd_config 中设置 PermitRootLogin no 并限制可登录用户白名单作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91495920911490&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1471","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1159.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1159","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1159.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1159.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jxq7-hfp5-q37w/GHSA-jxq7-hfp5-q37w.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88640/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1159.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000409.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/280f76b10d0670f8b6c2dcb23b3656450c8b6abc/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1369.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1285","title":"Linux 内核 /dev/urandom 读取不可中断导致资源耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.1.132 及之前版本中存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过从 /dev/urandom 等随机设备读取大量数据触发该漏洞，由于读取操作在完成之前无法被中断，将导致系统 CPU 和内存资源被大量消耗，造成系统响应缓慢甚至崩溃。该漏洞需要本地用户权限才能利用，攻击门槛较低，影响所有运行受影响的 Linux 内核版本的系统。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1285"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.677","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.1.133 或更高版本，该版本已将对 /dev/urandom 的读取操作改为可中断（interruptible），避免单次大块读取耗尽 CPU 资源。如无法升级内核，可通过 ulimit 限制单进程可打开的最大文件描述符数量和 CPU 时间，降低本地拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91495921611500&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1472","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1285.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1285","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1285.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1285.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qwqh-r8x8-wh6j/GHSA-qwqh-r8x8-wh6j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84454/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1285.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1384","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1384.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1188","title":"MySQL mysqld 日志文件权限配置不当信息泄露漏洞","description":"MySQL 3.21 版本的 mysqld 守护进程以全局可读权限创建日志文件，导致添加至用户数据库的用户密码被记录并暴露给所有本地用户。本地攻击者可直接读取日志文件获取用户凭证，进而实现未授权数据库访问。该漏洞影响 MySQL 3.21 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1188"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.387","remediation":"升级 MySQL 至 3.23 及以上版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。配置 umask 限制日志文件权限为 640，确保 mysqld 日志目录仅对 mysql 用户和 dba 组可读。在 my.cnf 中设置 log-bin、log-error 等日志文件路径指向权限受限目录，并通过 chmod 640 定期审计日志文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91479159617803&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1568","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1188.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1188","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1188.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1188.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c8f9-m33j-ppw6/GHSA-c8f9-m33j-ppw6.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1188.yaml","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mysql_3_22.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88627/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/35c40c2c96029682f9c3da862749763b6c97e1fb/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-11xx/CVE-1999-1188.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000407.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1384.toml"}]